---
layout: base.njk
title: "Lessons — Built Not Consumed"
description: "Practical lessons on using AI to build, not to be consumed by it."
---

<header class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="mono">The playbook</span>
    <h1 class="display">Lessons</h1>
  </div>
</header>

<section style="padding-top:0;">
  <div class="wrap">
    {% if collections.lessons.length > 0 %}
    <div class="lesson-grid">
      {% for lesson in collections.lessons %}
      <a class="lesson-card" href="{{ lesson.url }}">
        <span class="mono">{{ lesson.data.date | date }}</span>
        <h3>{{ lesson.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ lesson.data.summary }}</p>
        <span class="read">Read &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty-state">First lessons are coming soon. <a href="/#signup">Get on the list</a> to catch them the moment they're live.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
